column1: #Text=Lin says : " How many of those things are you going to stick in me ? "
#Text=Guo says : " I 'll be placing several needles on each of your acu - points .
#Text=" Guo says : " Please , close your eyes and take a deep breath .
#Text=This process corrects an imbalance in your chi .
#Text=Please tell me if you feel any pain or pressure .
#Text=" Lin says : " I ca n't feel a thing .
#Text=Acupuncture often taps into peoples ' buried memories .
#Text=These memories can sometimes be difficult to process .
